{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign_congr\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">sign_congr</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">φs </span><span class=\"fn\">φs'</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h</span> : <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs'</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs'</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.congr\">congr</a> <span class=\"fn\">⋯</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign_congr","kind":"theorem","line":54,"name":"WickContraction.sign_congr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L54-L57"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign_empty\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">sign_empty</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.empty\">empty</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign_empty","kind":"theorem","line":49,"name":"WickContraction.sign_empty","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L49-L52"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">sign</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a list `φs` of `𝓕.FieldOp`, and a Wick contraction `φsΛ` of `φs`,\n  the complex number `φsΛ.sign` is defined to be the sign (`1` or `-1`) corresponding\n  to the number of `fermionic`-`fermionic` exchanges that must be done to put\n  contracted pairs within `φsΛ` next to one another, starting recursively\n  from the contracted pair\n  whose first element occurs at the left-most position.\n\n  As an example, if `[φ1, φ2, φ3, φ4]` correspond to fermionic fields then the sign\n  associated with\n- `{{0, 1}}` is `1`\n- `{{0, 1}, {2, 3}}` is `1`\n- `{{0, 2}, {1, 3}}` is `-1`\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign","kind":"def","line":32,"name":"WickContraction.sign","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L32-L47"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.signFinset\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">signFinset</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i1 </span><span class=\"fn\">i2</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Fin\">Fin</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Finset/Defs.html#Finset\">Finset</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Fin\">Fin</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a Wick contraction `c : WickContraction n` and `i1 i2 : Fin n` the finite set\nof elements of `Fin n` between `i1` and `i2` which are either uncontracted\nor are contracted but are contracted with an element occurring after `i1`.\nIn other words, the elements of `Fin n` between `i1` and `i2` which are not\ncontracted with before `i1`.\nOne should assume `i1 < i2` otherwise this finite set is empty. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.signFinset","kind":"def","line":22,"name":"WickContraction.signFinset","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L22-L30"}}],"imports":["Init","PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.WickContraction.Basic","PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.Koszul.KoszulSign"],"instances":[],"name":"PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.WickContraction.Sign.Basic"}